		"title": "Patterns of Modular Architecture (Workshop) - Part 1",
		"summary": "Monolithic applications are difficult to understand, maintain, and extend with new features and functionality. Modularity helps achieve these goals. Unfortunately, few applications have been designed with modularity in mind. In this workshop, we take a deep dive into modularity. ",
