		"title": "10 Ways of Architecting Applications for the Cloud",
		"summary": "We make many assumptions when we develop our applications. Many of these assumptions no longer hold true when we start to build applications for the cloud. Cloud platforms also introduce architectural possibilities that do not exist in traditional deployment settings. This session will examine ten areas that we can architect our applications differently to prepare them for the unique characteristics of cloud environments.",
