		"summary": "The Spock framework brings simple, elegant testing to Java and Groovy projects.  It integrates cleanly with JUnit, so Spock tests can be integrated as part of an existing test suite.  Spock also includes an embedded mocking framework that can be used right away.",
		"detail": "In this presentation, we'll look at several examples of Spock tests and review most of its capabilities, including mock objects and integration with Spring.",
